@startuml seq_28_handle_global_reports
title Sequence Diagram: UC-28 Handle Global Reports

actor Admin
participant "Admin Web" as Frontend
participant "Admin Report Controller" as Controller
participant "Report Service" as Service
participant "Report Repo" as Repo

Admin -> Frontend: (1.1) Open Global Reports Dashboard
Frontend -> Controller: (2.1) GET /api/admin/reports?filter=...
Controller -> Service: (6.1) Get Reports
Service -> Repo: (5.1) Validate Admin Access
Repo --> Service: (5.2) Access valid
Service -> Repo: (6.2) Fetch filtered reports
Repo --> Service: (6.3) List of Reports
Service --> Controller: (7.1) Reports Data
Controller --> Frontend: (7.2) 200 OK
Frontend --> Admin: (7.3) Display reports table

Admin -> Frontend: (3.1/4.1) Select report(s) & Click Delete
Frontend -> Controller: (4.2) DELETE /api/admin/reports {report_ids}
Controller -> Service: (8.1) Delete Reports
Service -> Repo: (5.3) Validate Admin Access
Repo --> Service: (5.4) Access valid
Service -> Repo: (8.2) Soft/Hard delete selected report records
Repo --> Service: (8.3) Reports deleted
Service --> Controller: (9.1) Success
Controller --> Frontend: (9.2) 200 OK
Frontend --> Admin: (9.3) Remove reports from dashboard UI
@enduml
